    ‚àÉ t, s ‚äÜ t ‚àß MeasurableSet t ‚àß ‚àÄ i, Œº i t = (Œº i).trim s := by
  choose t hst ht hŒºt using fun i => (Œº i).exists_measurable_superset_eq_trim s
